OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud during Monday
OL,7,Fmorning. However, increasing amounts
OL,8,Fof sunshine are likely to develop into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy overnight and dry,
OL,12,Fwith some occasional breaks in the
OL,13,Fcloud. Winds becoming light and
OL,14,Fvariable with some fog patches
OL,15,Fpossible by the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FTuesday will be dry with
OL,18,Flight winds. Cloudy for the most with
OL,19,Fsome occasional sunny spells during
OL,20,Fthe afternoon. Widespread fog patches
OL,21,Flikely overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
