OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFoggy
OL,6,Fstart becoming cloudy with light winds
OL,7,Fon Wednesday. Morning fog will quickly
OL,8,Fclear on Thursday becoming cloudy
OL,9,Flater. Remaining cloudy on Friday with
OL,10,Fpatchy rain and drizzle.
